SimpleURLAPI - Interface in com.pega.pegarules.pub.simpleurl

SimpleURLAPI
This Interface provides API to generate Simple URL as defined in URLMapping.
API differ in criteria they use for choosing URLMapping.
This URLMapping is chosen from a list defined on application's Rule-URLMapppings instance.
Simple URL unless explicitly stated contains only path part of a Absolute URL and leaves out the servlet name as well.
